en-us.text_body:
Would you like to enable Mobile Apps on SYNC?

To use Mobile Apps with SYNC, SYNC will communicate with Ford at least once per month using your mobile devices data plan. Standard rates may apply. SYNC will send your VIN and SYNC module number to Ford U.S.

Updates are about the size of an email, and the occurrence of updates depends on your vehicle usage and when a new app is found on your device. To turn on or off, visit the SYNC Settings menu. See your Owner Guide for more information.
